				\begin{document}$${\overrightarrow{\tau }}_{{\rm{STT}}}$$\end{document}τ→STT). This equation was numerically solved using the fourth-order Runge-Kutta method. The simulated p-MTJ is composed of a Ta/CoFeB/MgO/CoFeB multilayer. The parameters considered in these simulations are given in Table 1.
